{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","title":"setResourceBasePath(resourcePath:)","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:3GIO19ApplicationProtocolPAAE19setResourceBasePath08resourceG0ySPys4Int8VGSg_tF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO11ApplicationC","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setResourceBasePath","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"resourcePath","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar","text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">?)"}],"extendedModule":"GIO"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/ApplicationProtocol-Implementations"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets (or unsets) the base resource path of ","type":"text"},{"code":"application","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setResourceBasePath"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"resourcePath"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar","text":"gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">? = nil)"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The path is used to automatically load various"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#struct@Gio.Resource","isActive":true},{"text":" such as menu layouts and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"action descriptions. The various types of resources will be found at","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"fixed names relative to the given base path."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the resource base path is determined from the application"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ID by prefixing ‘\/’ and replacing each ‘.’ with ‘\/’.  This is done at","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the time that the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object is constructed.  Changes to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the application ID after that point will not have an impact on the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resource base path."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As an example, if the application has an ID of “org.example.app” then"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the default resource base path will be “\/org\/example\/app”.  If this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GtkApplication"},{"text":" (and you have not manually changed the path)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then Gtk will then search for the menus of the application at","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"“\/org\/example\/app\/gtk\/menus.ui”.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Resource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" for more information about adding resources to your"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"application.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can disable automatic resource loading functionality by setting","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the path to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the resource base path once the application is running is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"not recommended.  The point at which the resource path is consulted","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for forming paths for various purposes is unspecified.  When writing"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a sub-class of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" you should either set the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application","isActive":true},{"text":" property at construction time, or call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"this function during the instance initialization. Alternatively, you"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can call this function in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GApplicationClass.startup"},{"type":"text","text":" virtual function,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"before chaining up to the parent implementation."}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/application\/setresourcebasepath(resourcepath:)"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Application\/setResourceBasePath(resourcePath:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"https://docs.gtk.org/gtk4/class.Builder.html":{"type":"link","title":"GtkBuilder","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GtkBuilder"}],"url":"https:\/\/docs.gtk.org\/gtk4\/class.Builder.html","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.gtk.org\/gtk4\/class.Builder.html"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/Application/ApplicationProtocol-Implementation